data.description: This raised ranch home boasts a captivating presence with its clean lines and inviting facade. Ascending the steps to the entrance, you're greeted by a quaint porch just waiting for someone to make it their own. Upon entering, the main level unfolds seamlessly, revealing an open-concept layout bathed in natural light streaming through expansive windows, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. Adjacent to the living area, the gourmet kitchen beckons with its sleek cabinetry & stainless steel appliances. A large center island offers both additional prep space and a casual dining spot, while the adjoining dining area provides ample room for hosting dinner parties or family meals. Glass sliding doors lead to a sprawling deck overlooking the picturesque backyard, where lush greenery and mature trees create a private oasis perfect for outdoor entertaining or quiet retreats.With its harmonious blend of contemporary design, functional layout, and serene surroundings, this raised ranch home epitomizes modern living at its finest, offering both comfort and sophistication for its fortunate inhabitants. Schedule your showing today!
